Package nl.mtvehicles.core.infrastructure.dependencies

package nl.mtvehicles.core.infrastructure.dependencies
Classes containing methods for plugin's supported soft-dependencies.
Beware!
Do not initialise classes directly. Use DependencyModule's fields instead.
